            <p>O <span xlink:href="urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689!art387_cpt_inc4">inciso IV do art. 387 do Decreto-Lei nº 3.689 de 3 de outubro de 1941</span> passa a vigorar com a seguinte redação:</p>
            <Alteracao xml:base="urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689" id="art1_cpt_alt1">
              <!--Matches: MatchResult(Map(urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689 -> MatchByBase(urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689,1941,Some((10,3)),Map(art387 -> SuperPrefixMatch(URN(1941,Some((10,3)),art387_cpt_inc4,urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689!art387_cpt_inc4),art387), art387_cpt -> SuperPrefixMatch(URN(1941,Some((10,3)),art387_cpt_inc4,urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689!art387_cpt_inc4),art387_cpt), art387_cpt_inc4 -> ExactMatch(URN(1941,Some((10,3)),art387_cpt_inc4,urn:lex:br:federal:decreto.lei:1941-10-03;3689!art387_cpt_inc4))))))-->
